# 🗂️ Windows File Server and NTFS Permissions Lab

## 📋 Overview
Built a Windows File Server environment to simulate how organizations manage shared resources and control access to sensitive data using NTFS and Share permissions.

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Windows Server 2022
- Active Directory
- NTFS Permissions
- Shared Folders
- Oracle VirtualBox

## 🎯 Objectives
- Create shared folders
- Configure NTFS permissions
- Configure Share permissions
- Apply least privilege access
- Test user access
- Configure file auditing

